item.title: I run my compile, jar.do not work..., run.bat not working please help
item.dc:creator: @Codesoft Codesoft
item.description:
@Codesoft wrote:

Here this is one of the best run.bat’s.

[code]@ECHO OFF
title Client Start

:info
CLS
ECHO !!!run.bat!!!
ECHO Updating Client By: Ash
ECHO --------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ECHO Type run to start the run.bat.
ECHO Type Exit to Exit.
SET option=
ECHO.
SET /p option=Choose an option.
if %option%==run goto runclient
if %option%==Exit exit

:runclient
CLS
java -Xmx1024m -cp .;./jython.jar;./MySql/mysql-connector-java-3.0.17-ga-bin.jar client
PAUSE
CLS
GOTO info

java -Xmx500m -jar client.jar 0 0 highmem members 0
pause
PAUSE
GOTO info

[/code]
